l determines your survival. Are you ready to DodgeALL?", "short_description": "DodgeALL is an adrenaline-fueled VR game that tests your reflexes in immersive 3D environments. With physics-based gameplay, each level is a new challenge. Can you weave, dodge, and survive in an arena where everyone is throwing things at you?"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://dodgeall.com/PrivacyPolicy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "GlennerooVR LLC", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.dodgeall.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "1592192974313489"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "7267329153368602"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 2, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1251385075979902"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1231507447541804"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1231507447541804"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1734724800, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1251385075979902"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "8078220658946110", "version": "0.40.7.1"}, "id": "2493148167513843", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5477835475651321", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8078220658946110"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "2493148167513843"}]}, "change_log": "VERSION: 0.40.7.1\nBUGFIX: Camera is no longer locked to floor at startup!\nBUGFIX: Skyboxes are now visible again (regression due to All-In-One SDK default settings).\nINTERNAL: Updated to Meta XR All-in-One SDK 71.0.0.", "created_date": 1733066492, "id": "8078220658946110", "version": "0.40.7.1", "version_code": 615, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5477835475651321", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8078220658946110"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "2493148167513843"}]}, "change_log": "VERSION: 0.40.7.0\nBUGFIX: ScoreBoard header titles are now consistent and grammatically correct.\nBUGFIX: Pirates campaign now plays arena ambience audio.\nBUGFIX: Level ratings now save username correctly.\nBUGFIX: Removed Oculus Spatializer reflections.\nBUGFIX: Endless mode > style score calculation takes into account total number of obstacles.\nBUGFIX: Endless mode now resets all portals/worlds back to original state of level after finishing the level instance.\nCHANGE: Made arrows in Level Rating panel bigger.\nCHANGE: Order of level ratings changed to be more logical.\nCHANGE: No style points for obstacles that are dodged when > 5m away.", "created_date": 1732912089, "id": "8069174953184014", "version": "0.40.7.0", "version_code": 607, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5477835475651321", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8078220658946110"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "2493148167513843"}]}, "change_log": "VERSION: 0.40.6.0\nBUGFIX: Obstacles now play audio correctly when moving (huge regression in 40.2.0)!!!\nBUGFIX: Arena ambience ambisonic audio now plays correctly when teleporting.\nBUGFIX: Cleaned up SciFiHardwareStore world.\nBUGFIX: Shield tutorial level can now be completed after blocking 2 obstacles.\nBUGFIX: Tutorial now shows correct controllers for all Quest devices.\nCHANGE: Changed some tutorial level text to be less confusing.", "created_date": 1732494311, "id": "8043611465740363", "version": "0.40.6.0", "version_code": 606, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5477835475651321", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8078220658946110"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "2493148167513843"}]}, "change_log": "VERSION: 0.40.5.0\nFEATURE: Added level rating screen in Scoreboard.\nFEATURE: Endless mode now shows how long (seconds) player survived.\nFEATURE: Endless mode Leaderboards now show time instead of points.\nFEATURE: Added new Endless mode achievements.\nFEATURE: Endless scoreboard now shows how many obstacles dodged.\nCHANGE: SciFi > Virus02 now clones in a different direction.\nCHANGE: Starting level UI now shows if Endless or Campaign; same with ScoreBoard.\nCHANGE: Aborting Endless level no longer adds score to leaderboard.\nCHANGE: SciFi > Crystal now spawns clones in random directions.\nBUGFIX: ScrapFan clones now separate correctly.\nBUGFIX: Maximum obstacle speed correctly implemented for endless mode and custom level files.\nBUGFIX: Closest possible dodge distance is now 0.01 instead of 0.\nBUGFIX: Clones launched from 45-degree portals now slide correctly to position relative to parent.\nBUGFIX: Achievement Unlocked description no longer chops text in 2nd line.\nBUGFIX: Pressing Settings > Reset or Player > Reset buttons now return to Main Menu after resetting settings.", "created_date": 1732393705, "id": "8037774402990736", "version": "0.40.5.0", "version_code": 603, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5477835475651321", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8078220658946110"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "2493148167513843"}]}, "change_log": "FEATURE: Added new SciFi Campaign #2 levels 5-8 and Bonus #2; all other levels should no longer cause errors but are still WIP.\nBUGFIX: Some obstacles now no longer collide with some types or all other obstacles.\nCHANGE: Increased time of Achievement Unlocked pop-up to 5 seconds.\nCHANGE: SciFi > TrashBag now explodes into trash. The player can not dodge this trash and it causes no harm.\nCHANGE: Replaced SciFi > Scrap1 with new ScrapPipe; now \"boomerangs\" back from platform edge.\nCHANGE: Replaced SciFi > Scrap2 with new ScrapFan which rotates very quickly.\nCHANGE: Obstacles now allowed to target player lower.", "created_date": 1730928916, "id": "7946119265489584", "version": "0.40.4.0", "version_code": 601, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}]}}, "viewer": {"user": null}}}